      <hedline>
        <hl1>BROADCOM BEATS ESTIMATES</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Broadcom Corp says earnings were $55.9 million, compared with $20.1 million a year earlier; revenue climbed to $245.2 million from $119.5 million (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Broadcom Corporation, citing strong demand for its communications chips, said it earned 22 cents a share in the second quarter, beating analysts' estimates of 19 cents. Earnings were $55.9 million, compared with $20.1 million a year earlier. Revenue climbed to $245.2 million from $119.5 million.</p>
      </block>
